resources.name: Player
Cute Game Assets
resources.description:
This is a set of cute game assets that Seth designed for a course he taught over the summer.

Included:
5 Characters (Front, iso, side, and back view)
17 Enemies (Front and side view)
31 Game assets (Front view)

Feel free to use these assets in your game
